claim.claim-text:
1. A method for producing an item list if components for assembling a module, comprising the steps of: 
at a first location, providing an inventory of components for use in assembling a module, and providing each of said components with a reference number, said components being accessible from said first location; 
storing the respective reference numbers of said components together with at least one individual property of each of said components in a databank disposed at a second location which is different from said first location; 
generating an inquiry at said first location for producing an item list including designated components among said components at said first location; 
communicating said inquiry from said first location to said second location; 
dependent on said inquiry and dependent on the respective individual properties and reference numbers of the components stored in said databank producing said item list at said second location, said item list including a property of the designated components and the respective reference numbers of the designated components; and 
communicating said item list from said second location to said first location.

2. A method as claimed in claim 1 comprising the additional steps of: 
assembling said module at said first location based on said item list to produce an assembled module; 
checking the components comprising said assembled module at said first location as to operability to obtain check data respectively allocated to the components in the assembled module; 
transmitting said check data to said second location and identifying faulty components, among the components in said assembled module, at said second location dependent on said check data; 
at said second location, identifying respective replacement components for each component identified as faulty in said assembled module, from the components still available in said inventory, using said property stored in said databank; and 
at said second location, identifying respective number for said replacement components and communicating the reference numbers of the replacement components from said second location to said first location.
